(14, 1, '2012-08-15 08:59:10', '2012-08-15 08:59:10', 'Dr Adamcik is a licensed physician of the state of Florida. He trained at New Jersey Medical School and did advanced training in Internal medicine at Loma Linda University and the prestigious Scripps Clinic in San Diego California. He is board certified in Internal Medicine.\r\n\r\nThrough the years Dr Adamcik had been frustrated by the medical fields’ lack of attention to dietary treatment and has made a lifelong study of healthy diets. This resulted in the publishing of his book “The Globes Best diet” and his first weight loss clinic in Palm Bay Florida in 2009.\r\n\r\nDr Adamcik has trained in cosmetics treatments including advanced Botox, filler and laser treatments and had been practicing these procedures in his Palm Bay clinic since 2008.\r\n\r\nDr Adamcik has attended numerous anti-aging conferences, and is an associate member of A4m, the anti-aging academy of America.  He continues to do independent research in this area and he is on the cutting edge of therapies.<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>His office locations</strong>\r\n<ul class="left">\r\n	<li>Renew Youth</li>\r\n	<li>222 USHWY 1</li>\r\n	<li>Suite 5</li>\r\n	<li>Tequesta, FL, 33469</li>\r\n	<li>561-401-9892</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.renew-youth.com/">www.renew-youth.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="mailto:contact@renew-youth.com">contact@renew-youth.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="left">\r\n	<li>Adamcik  Medical</li>\r\n	<li>580 Malabar Road</li>\r\n	<li>Suite 2</li>\r\n	<li>Palm Bay, FL, 32907</li>\r\n	<li>321-327-2980</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.dradamcik.com/">www.dradamcik.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>nicholeambrosino@cfl.rr.com</li>\r\n</ul>', 'About <span>Dr. <span>Adamcik</span></span>', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-dr-adamcik', '', '', '2012-08-15 09:46:26', '2012-08-15 09:46:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/renew-youth/?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
